{
  "texts": [
    "Among those who self-report their age, around 46% of the messages in our dataset are accounted for by users 18-25.",
    "We study global patterns of ChatGPT usage by measuring the proportion of weekly consumer Chat-GPT users among the internet enabled population of countries with populations larger than 1 million.",
    "We also exclude countries in which ChatGPT is blocked.",
    "The figure below plots this proportion in May 2024 and May 2025 by GDP-per-capita deciles: countries are ranked by GDP-per-capita and split into ten deciles, and the x-axis shows each decile's median GDP-per-capita (in thousands of U.S. dollars).",
    "24 The solid line shows the median share within each decile; the shaded band is the interquartile range (25th-75th percentile) of country values within that decile."
  ]
}